I have two Beagles! Not show dogs..but we love them..they were both rescue
cases. I enjoy going to the dog show thats held at the Arena building here
in Cape just to see all the different breeds..fun! I grew up with hounds..my
Dad raised Beagles and Walker Coonhounds..I treked many a night thru the
woods trying to keep up with my Dad following the sound of the hounds cry.
We had mini mules that we rode sometimes too.
Julie in MO
